eu.first.RIM

Class RIMdata

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.first.RIM.RIMdata

  • public class RIMdata
extends java.lang.Object
    RIMdata class. Stores data manipulated by RIMmodel class. Data corresponds to a single product/customer pair. Data includes both input data, which represent value arguments for a single run of RIMmodel, and output results, obtained by RIMmodel evaluation.
    Since:
    2012-10-20
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Marko Bohanec (marko.bohanec@ijs.si)
